41void vp8_start_encode(BOOL_CODER *bc, unsigned char *source,
42 unsigned char *source_end) {
43 bc->lowvalue = 0;
44 bc->range = 255;
45 bc->count = -24;
46 bc->buffer = source;
47 bc->buffer_end = source_end;
48 bc->pos = 0;
49}
50
51void vp8_stop_encode(BOOL_CODER *bc) {
52 int i;
53
54 for (i = 0; i < 32; ++i) vp8_encode_bool(bc, 0, 128);
55}
56
57void vp8_encode_value(BOOL_CODER *bc, int data, int bits) {
58 int bit;
59
60 for (bit = bits - 1; bit >= 0; bit--) {
61 vp8_encode_bool(bc, (1 & (data >> bit)), 0x80);
62 }
63}
